title: Cant see owned champions?
body: I own volibear as you can see by my match history have 8 games on him that ive won and for some reason just not cant pick him in champ select

replies.body: Checked your account and it looks like the recent gifts received by your account (including Volibear) were reversed due to issues with the gifting account.  Can't provide too many details on those issues since it's another account, but if you have other questions about your account I'm happy to answer if I can.
